ide the outer while loop block, it makes sense to declare it there. Remember, declare your variables in the smallest scope possible!Question #2Write a program that prints out the letters a through z along with their ASCII codes. Use a loop variable of typechar.Show HintHint: To print characters as integers, you have to use a static_cast.Show Solution#include <iostream>

